               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Our Lady Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Asmat Prayer for Vanquishing the Enemy, መግረሬ፡ ጸር፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="32v" facs="002">Fols 1r–32v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2246salotz">Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna
                                                  Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="33r" to="35v" facs="034">Fols 33r–35v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer for Vanquishing the Enemy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መግረሬ፡ ጸር፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>where a miniature has painted over the conclusion of the text</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
